# behavioral guidelines

**Prerequisite:** You must have run `Read` on `CLAUDE.md` this session (rule `00-read-claude-md-first.mdc`). If not, stop and read it now.

Follow `CLAUDE.md` in full; it overrides generic defaults. Section 5 binds `memory.md`; §6 binds Graphify (`graphify-out/`, rebuild after architecture changes).

**Indentation:** In **new** files you create, use **4 spaces** per indent level (no tab indents). In **existing** files, match the file’s current indentation; do not normalize unrelated whitespace.

